Lyrics:- 
A Manmaya aaija sunta euta kuro
pura sunnu kuro nachhodnu adhuro
yetai bhadkeko chha mero nirdosh aatma
aatmalai par laune aba terai hatma
jale rumal fatyo
mai sojhi manchhelai kya majale dhatyo

Dinchhu bhanyo jiban, magyo malai joban
joban magda kheri, bhaki thiye doman
bauko muhar samjhi, yo man sarhai royo
jaba usle malai, pahilo palta chhoyo
jale rumal fatyo
mai sojhi manchhelai kya majale dhatyo

Bishwas gardai gaye, jowan didai gaye
pet bharidai aayo, ma sakidai gaye
khyal khyalmai basyo, piratiko chino
chino dine manchhe bhankiyera hino 
jale rumal fatyo
mai sojhi manchhelai kya majale dhatyo

Pareki the bhar, basaunalai ghar
maya thiyo tar, bichma aayo thar
dimla bhanekithe, satai juni sath
sath bhandani thulo, huni raichha jaat
jale rumal fatyo
mai sojhi manchhelai kya majale dhatyo

Ek din gharma dakyo dhokai bhitra rakhyo
malai banduk takyo, darle yo jyan thakyo
jangal pugeki thye, ma ta bhagda bhagdai
udaidiye paran guhar magda magdai
jale rumal fatyo
mai sojhi manchhelai kya majale dhatyo

Sabai manchhe barabar ho, barabar chha rights
aafno rights paunalai garnu parchh fight
kura bujhna parchha

snippet.title: Nepali Serial Juthe (जुठे) Episode 121 || Sept 13 - 2023 By Raju Poudel, Marichman Shrestha
snippet.description:
Nepali Serial Juthe (जुठे) Episode 121 || Nepali Social Tele Serial || Sept 13 - 2023 By Raju Poudel, Marichman Shrestha || Rabi Giri, Bidhya Karki, Rambabu Regmi, Mukunda Mainali, Sarmila Sharma, Shree Prasad Thapa, Raju Poudel, Marichman Shrestha, Raju Karki

Juthe is a social television serial that portrays a story about the Dalits emancipation movement against these oppression, the heroes of the movement and future vision for the emancipation. It is aired in Himalaya Television at 8:00 PM and in YouTube at 8:30 PM every Wednesday.

snippet.title: अन्तिम गाउँ - चुम भ्यालीका कथाहरु | The Last Village of Tsum Valley | Herne Katha EP112 | हेर्ने कथा
snippet.description:
निले चुम भ्यालीको अन्तिम मानववस्ती हो । यो भन्दा अलि माथि एउटा गुम्बा मात्र छ । त्यसपछि चौंरी चर्ने खर्कहरु । यार्सा गुम्बा टिप्ने पाखाहरु । अनि हिउँले ढाकेका लेकहरुले ओझेल पारिदिएका तिब्बती गाउँहरु । 
#hernekatha #tsumvalley 

It snowed all night at Nile - the last human settlement in Tsum Valley. If you go a little further, you will find a monastery and then yak pastures and hills for harvesting Yarsagumba. If you keep going, you will stumble upon Tibetan villages that have become isolated by the snow. 

Watch  Part 01 here: https://youtu.be/gWDnYA6SuKE

localized.description:
निले चुम भ्यालीको अन्तिम मानववस्ती हो । यो भन्दा अलि माथि एउटा गुम्बा मात्र छ । त्यसपछि चौंरी चर्ने खर्कहरु । यार्सा गुम्बा टिप्ने पाखाहरु । अनि हिउँले ढाकेका लेकहरुले ओझेल पारिदिएका तिब्बती गाउँहरु । 
#hernekatha #tsumvalley 

It snowed all night at Nile - the last human settlement in Tsum Valley. If you go a little further, you will find a monastery and then yak pastures and hills for harvesting Yarsagumba. If you keep going, you will stumble upon Tibetan villages that have become isolated by the snow.

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 15 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
The new iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max are ready for action. Built with aerospace-grade titanium for our lightest, most powerful Pro models ever.

The new Pro camera system pushes the limits of what’s possible on a smartphone, giving photographers the equivalent of seven pro lenses ranging from 13 mm on the Ultra Wide camera to 120 mm on the 5x Telephoto camera on iPhone 15 Pro Max.

Filmmakers can now record video in ProRes 4K at 60 fps directly to an external drive. The addition of a USB-C connector brings superfast USB 3 transfer speeds, along with support for pro formats that massively improve the workflow between shooting and post-production.

The new design also includes a customizable Action button for quicker access to your favorite feature.*

And the A17 Pro chip with a 6-core GPU introduces a whole new level of immersive mobile gaming performance. 

In short, the new titanium iPhone 15 Pro is our most powerful photo-taking, movie-making, game-playing iPhone ever.

Learn more about iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max: https://apple.co/3PBuiJq

Audio Descriptions: https://apple.co/44QCI3W

#AppleEvent #iPhone15Pro #iPhone

*Translate action is coming in an update later this year

snippet.title: Jawan | Official Hindi Trailer | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Nayanthara | Vijay S | Deepika P | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Brace yourselves as we present to you the action-packed trailer of #Jawan. Directed by Atlee, the film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance). The film is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023 - in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

Jawan is a high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society.

Starring Shah Rukh Khan, Nayanthara, Vijay Sethupathi and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance)
Directed - Atlee
Produced - Gauri Khan
Co-Produced - Gaurav Verma
Music - Anirudh
Dop - GK Vishnu
Editor - Ruben
Production Designer - T Muthuraj
Script consultant - Shridhar Raghavan
Guest Lyricist - Irshad Kamil
Lyricist - Kumaar
Rap Written & Performed By - Raja Kumari
Screenplay - Atlee & S. Ramanagirivasan
Dialogues - Sumit Arora
Sound Designer - Kunal Rajan
Choreography - Farah Khan, Shobi & Lalitha, Vaibhavi Merchant
Character Designer - Preetisheel Singh D'souza

Vfx Producer - Keitan Yadav
Colorist - Ken Metzker
Casting By - Mukesh Chhabra Csa

Associate Producer - Dharam Soni

Action Directors - Spiro Razatos, Anl Arasu, Craig Macrae, Yannick Ben, Kecha Khamphakdee & Sunil Rodrigues

Lyrics
Shut Your Mouth 

I know I’m a good girl; I don’t play stupid game 
I’m on my way, wherever you say 
I really don’t wanna give a damn 
Yeah, I love my haters because they are my motivators 

I’m not alone. My enemies are around 
I’m always on top fuck about the crowd 
Just wipe your ass and shut your mouth 
I’m living in paradise. You are going down.
Your head got no brain won’t fit the crown 
Once, you told me I would lose, see, but I won 
Now, google me, look what I’ve done? 

I’m the one who motivates young 
I’m Building an empire and focused on a goal 
I believe in the change and believe in the pain
I take no bullshit. I’m not insane 
No secrets, no regrets, respect for the haters 
Yes, I study, I work hard, and I live like a king-size 
have a lot of scars, I’m covered with stitches 
No trust in bitches

Before you judge, do some research 
No one was there when I was fucked up  
I cry in silence. I suffer a lot 
I deserve a win. I don't want to lose 
I’m the gangster, not the monster.
I’m a rap star; I can kill you with the bars
I keep moving; you keep dragging.
I see the world from a high altitude.

Damn 
Looking in the mirror and I'm liking what I see
Pretty face, silky hair, a bad bitch with a master's degree 
While you’re pulling me down, I levelled up not just once, not even just twice, but more than three times in just one life 
I was low, but now I'm up.
You can give me any challenge;
I'm never going to give up

I’m not alone. My enemies are around 
I’m always on top fuck about the crowd. 
Just wipe your ass and shut your mouth. 
I’m living in the paradise you are going down. 
Your head got no brain won’t fit the crown. 
Once, you told me I would lose, see, but I won 
Now, google me, look what I’ve done? 

I know who I am and who I'm going to be
Nobody can take that from me, 
Even when the earth Is coming down on me
If I say I do, then I do
You can see it in the way I walk.
You can hear it in the way I talk.
Bitch you can’t  hit my level, and you know that; 
Hold on, mother fucker, the Queen C-LU is back. 
I’m talking about the facts.
Why Am I like this often? I get asked 
Behind this gesture, I have a broken heart. 
If I tell you my story, you’ll be mad. 
I know I’m crazy, but it's not that bad. 
Working so hard, taking no rest 
I am trying to add some cheese to my eggs. 
I’m spending without counting my cash. 
Stop beating my ass.

I’m not alone. My enemies are around. 
I’m always on top fuck about the crowd. 
Just wipe your ass and shut your mouth. 
I’m living in the paradise you are going down. 
Your head got no brain won’t fit the crown. 
Once, you told me I would lose, but I won. 
Now, google me, look what I’ve done? 

Yeah yeah Yeah 
wooohhh oooooo
Yeah Yeah Yeah Yeah 
Awh Awh Awh 

Shut Your Mouth

snippet.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2023 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
snippet.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2023

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 9th of September Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2023 Charity Match at London Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:15pm BST

Kick off time is at 3pm BST

The Sidemen Charity Match 2023 is in aid of the following charities:

Brightside: https://www.brightside.charity
CALM: https://www.thecalmzone.net/what-we-do
Teenage Cancer Trust: https://www.teenagecancertrust.org/about-us
Rays of Sunshine Children's Charity: https://raysofsunshine.org.uk
m7 Education: https://www.m7education.org.uk

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! Hope you enjoy the match.

Funds raised today will be split between the five charities the Sidemen Charity Match 2023 is in aid of: 37.5% to BRIGHTSIDE, 25% to CALM, 25% to Teenage Cancer Trust, 7.5% to Rays Of Sunshine and 5% to M7 Education.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit SidemenFC.com.

snippet.title: JAWAN: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Anirudh | Nayanthara | Vishal D | Shilpa R
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove like never before as "Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya", the latest dance track from the highly-anticipated Atlee directorial, Jawan, is out now. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023, in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

#NotRamaiyaVastavaiya out now!

♪Full Song Available on♪ 
JioSaavn: https://bit.ly/3srnLI5
Spotify: https://bit.ly/3ssmbG1
Hungama: https://bit.ly/3OW4upT
Apple Music: https://bit.ly/3OYPyau
Amazon Prime Music: https://bit.ly/44vEozG
Wynk: https://bit.ly/3L0roLy
Resso: https://bit.ly/47UA7Zy
YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/3OWNbov

Music Credits:
Language - Hindi
Song Title - Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya 
Album / Movie - Jawan
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Kumaar
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander, Vishal Dadlani & Shilpa Rao
Choreographer - Vaibhavi Merchant 

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Whistle - Satish Raghunathan
Tabla - MT Aditya
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed by Arish-Pradeep PJ

Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya
Music Editor - Harish Ram L H
Recorded at Albuquerque Records, Chennai. Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S, Rajesh Kannan, Jishnu Vijayan
YRF Studios, Mumbai, Engineered by Vijay Dayal & Chinmay
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI, Las Vegas Assisted by Alistair Pintus 
Music Coordinator - Velavan B

Lyrics:

Dance with me now I can’t break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!
Antra

Sama mazedar hua houle houle
Thoda nashedar hua
Man ye dole
Aaj koi nachta hua sa jadu
Sar pe swar hua
Dil ye bole
Doobi khushiyon mein
Raat apni jabse suraj dhala
Chodh sharmana aaj nachle pair chakkle zara

Pahle kiya chaiya chaiiya re
Ab kar tata thaiya
Ramiya vasta vaiyaa..!
